Version: 1.0.0
Release Date: 2026-01-07
Codename: Foundation
Status: Stable
Compatibility: ai-pack 1.x

## Release Notes

This is the foundational release of the ai-pack framework, introducing a comprehensive multi-agent AI workflow system alongside established clean-code standards.

### New Features
- Multi-agent workflow framework with gates, roles, workflows, and task-packet templates
- Quality gates for controlling and validating agent actions
- Role definitions for orchestrator, worker, and reviewer agents
- Structured workflows for standard, feature, bugfix, refactor, and research tasks
- Task-packet templates for structured task management

### Clean Code Standards
- Universal design principles and SOLID principles
- Language-specific guidelines for C++, Python, JavaScript, Java, and Kotlin
- Comprehensive refactoring, testing, and architecture guidance
- Deployment patterns and development best practices

## Version History
- 1.0.0 (2026-01-07): Initial release with AI workflow framework
